          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Thank you to everyone who’s written in so far with thoughtful, considered questions, and puns and rants. Posting an email address on the internet is an invitation for disaster, but ",
            "type": "text",
